(WHIP CRACKS)

11
0:0:59.127 --> 0:1:0.762
And the phantom butterflies?

12
0:1:0.796 --> 0:1:2.530
You will experience episodes...

13
0:1:2.564 --> 0:1:3.798
lapses of clarity.

14
0:1:3.832 --> 0:1:5.901
You'll be back to normal soon.

15
0:1:6.502 --> 0:1:8.638
(GRUNTING)

16
0:1:21.016 --> 0:1:23.019
Whoo.

17
0:1:23.051 --> 0:1:25.554
I feel like a tornado
in a trailer park.

18
0:1:25.587 --> 0:1:30.492
CHOIR:
♪ Golden Circle proudly presents ♪

19
0:1:30.524 --> 0:1:33.494
Mr. President,
my name is Poppy Adams.

20
0:1:33.528 --> 0:1:36.731
I believe the UN has no teeth.

21
0:1:36.766 --> 0:1:38.567
So I've selected you,
as leader of the free world,

22
0:1:38.600 --> 0:1:40.468
to receive this communication.

23
0:1:40.502 --> 0:1:42.170
And I invite you
to begin negotiations...

24
0:1:42.203 --> 0:1:46.240
on the largest scale
hostage situation in history.

25
0:1:46.274 --> 0:1:47.475
A few weeks ago,

26
0:1:47.508 --> 0:1:49.311
an engineered virus
was released...

27
0:1:49.345 --> 0:1:52.146
contained in all
varieties of my product.

28
0:1:52.181 --> 0:1:56.651
Cannabis, cocaine, heroin,
opium, ecstasy...

29
0:1:56.685 --> 0:1:58.087
...and crystal meth.

30
0:1:59.355 --> 0:2:1.991
Some of you
are already infected.

31
0:2:2.024 --> 0:2:4.060
And this is what you can expect

32
0:2:4.092 --> 0:2:5.993
in the coming days.

33
0:2:6.028 --> 0:2:9.030
After a brief
incubation period...

34
0:2:9.064 --> 0:2:11.033
victims present
with stage one symptoms.

35
0:2:11.065 --> 0:2:12.367
(SNAPS FINGERS)

36
0:2:12.400 --> 0:2:13.602
A blue rash.

37
0:2:14.535 --> 0:2:15.636
Next...

38
0:2:15.669 --> 0:2:17.672
second stage symptoms appear.

39
0:2:17.706 --> 0:2:19.475
(SNAPS FINGERS) Mania...

40
0:2:19.507 --> 0:2:21.142
as the virus enters the brain.

41
0:2:21.176 --> 0:2:23.512
(WHISPERS)
Very distressing to the victim

42
0:2:23.544 --> 0:2:25.280
and those around them.

43
0:2:26.448 --> 0:2:27.749
Stage three... (SNAPS FINGERS)

44
0:2:29.117 --> 0:2:30.151
(GASPING)
Paralysis.

45
0:2:30.185 --> 0:2:33.055
Muscles enter a state
of catastrophic seizure.

46
0:2:33.088 --> 0:2:35.957
And once the muscles of
the thorax become affected...

47
0:2:35.992 --> 0:2:38.561
breathing becomes impossible...

48
0:2:38.593 --> 0:2:42.931
leading to a very nasty death
within 12 hours.

49
0:2:44.734 --> 0:2:49.938
But I have good news to
the millions already affected.

50
0:2:49.971 --> 0:2:51.706
It doesn't have to be this way.

51
0:2:51.740 --> 0:2:55.011
I have an antidote.

52
0:2:55.043 --> 0:2:56.177
(SNAPS FINGERS)

